summary: A fortified military presence in Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Adds stockade walls and more to Falkreath, Morthal, Ivastead, Winterhold, Shor\'s stone and Dragon bridge.
 my first mod ever so please add comments if you encounter bugs. This is a work in progress i will add more content later when i get the hang of the CK better. In future updates i will add more forts and the interiors for the forts in morthal and dragon bridge and several guards patrolling the surroundings=).

Update: I don\'t have the time to update this mod because life is a b*tch right now, you are welcome to mod and use it to suit your vision. I\'ve started with interiors in the CK, Every Cell ID starts with AB.
author: VGC
